hopobject.body: Another service? acai berry precio espaa One investigation led by Don Lewis, the dean at Hamline University's School of Law, found the slope failure was apparently due to natural soil erosion common along the Mississippi River bluffs, aggravated by a rainy spring and foot traffic along unmarked trails. The other investigation, led by Ryan Benson of Northern Technologies, Inc., found the rockslide was a result of natural environmental changes, combined with ongoing impacts of weather on sand and shale.
